snippet.title: Disciples Liberation - Official Gameplay Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
In this new gameplay trailer, Disciples Liberation lets you duel with demigods and seize your destiny. 270+ missions and 80 hours of gameplay await you in this dark fantasy strategy RPG.
